This if from ChatGPT:

| **Type**        | **Requirement**                                                                                                                   |
| --------------- | --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| Performance     | The system should return results quickly. Moving between login, 			profile view, and messaging should take no longer than 2 seconds. |
| Scalability     | Should handle 200+ users without crashing or slowing down.                                                                        |
| Portability     | Must run in Docker containers and deploy to AWS easily.                                                                           |
| Compatibility   | Works across modern browsers like Chrome, Firefox, and Safari.                                                                    |
| Reliability     | Must store and retrieve user/booking/message data reliably.                                                                       |
| Maintainability | Codebase should be modular and version-controlled (Git).                                                                          |
| Availability    | System should be live 99% of the time.                                                                                            |
| Security        | Passwords encrypted; PayPal must use secure authentication.                                                                       |
| Usability       | Interface should be clean, intuitive, and mobile-friendly.                                                                        |

